developed this module.  Contact us at cpan@clotho.com.


INSTALLATION

Install via one of the following:

  cpan install Devel::EnforceEncapsulation

or

  perl Build.PL
  perl Build
  perl Build test
  perl Build install

or

  perl Makefile.PL
  make
  make test
  make install
